{"tid":2450210,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"趙善軒 阿里巴巴斷翼！傳被迫出售《南華早報》等媒體， 中國與資本主義國家的根本差別！","createTime":"2021-03-17T08:28:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T08:28:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"072e2652fa81b84c7148b91678cd110df483f02f","tid":2450210,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:28:51.000Z","msg":"趙善軒<br />\n阿里巴巴斷翼！傳被迫出售《南華早報》等媒體，<br />\n中國與資本主義國家的根本差別！<br />\n20210317<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jQXcZutMh9Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjQXcZutMh9Q&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT8WiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=e814463c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jQXcZutMh9Q</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGavinchiu趙氏讀書生活<br />\n223K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n趙氏曾任教於美國Bryant University 、北京理工大學珠海學院、深圳大學、香港樹仁大學、臺灣中央研究院近史所等多間學府，歷任助理教授、副教授、研究員、客座教授、高級訪問學者；<br />\n<br />\n2018年獲中國經濟思想史優秀（一等）著作獎，研究題目包括經濟思想、經濟史、政治經濟學，出版著作二十一部，論文三十餘篇。英國權威出版社 Routledge給予 &quot;中國和西方頂尖學者（leading Chinese and Western scholar）&quot; 的評價。<br />\n<br />\n《趙氏讀書生活》，一個歷史學者的視頻，分享學術、社會、政治經濟觀察<br />\n收費平台可獲參考資料和專欄分享，請以每月5元或更多的美元支持：<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/Chiusreading​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2FChiusreading%E2%80%8B&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT8WiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=d42787aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/Chiusreading​</a><br />\n或於YOUTUBE 上按加入成為會員，可獲影片的參考資料<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCmi1...​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCmi1...%E2%80%8B&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT8WiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=ca197ccb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCmi1...​</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/drgavinchiu/​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdrgavinchiu%2F%E2%80%8B&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70